Ecology.Usages:
Many in the Realms were known to make strings for [[instruments]] from the dried intestines of rothé<ref>{{Cite web/theedverse/2020-06-06 - What Instrument Strings Are Made From}} and their horns were hollowed out and turned into drinking implements.

Rothé back steaks were a staple of [[dwarf|dwarven]] cuisine in the areas where the beasts were present.{{Cite web/theedverse/2022-11-03 - Dwarven Cuisine}}

Rothe where sheared for their wool.
